517
00:56:08,239 --> 00:56:09,699
Dia jelas menunggu saat ini.

518
00:56:10,533 --> 00:56:13,703
Kalian sedang di tengah skandal,
masyarakat membenci kalian,

519
00:56:13,787 --> 00:56:15,163
lalu dia mengirimkan ini.

520
00:56:17,040 --> 00:56:20,001
Mau bagaimana? Kita tak boleh diam saja.

521
00:56:27,050 --> 00:56:29,636
- Tolong berikan komentar!
- Jaksa Kwak!

522
00:56:29,719 --> 00:56:31,971
Kau mendakwa Do La-ik hari ini.

523
00:56:32,055 --> 00:56:35,767
Menurut laporan, ditemukan catatan
berisi pengakuan Choi Jae-hee.

524
00:56:35,850 --> 00:56:37,435
Apa alasanmu mendakwanya?

525
00:56:37,519 --> 00:56:39,604
Investigasi harus didasari bukti objektif.

526
00:56:39,687 --> 00:56:43,441
Kami telah mengamankan
bukti substansial fisik dan tak langsung,

527
00:56:43,525 --> 00:56:45,485
terlepas dari catatan Pak Choi Jae-hee,

528
00:56:45,568 --> 00:56:47,946
kami yakin akan meneruskan dakwaan.

529
00:56:48,029 --> 00:56:49,447
- Beri jalan.
- Jaksa Kwak!

530
00:56:49,531 --> 00:56:51,533
Tolong berikan satu komentar lagi!

531
00:56:51,616 --> 00:56:53,284
Berikan komentar singkat!

532
00:56:53,368 --> 00:56:54,702
Jangan pergi begitu saja!

533
00:56:54,786 --> 00:56:57,914
Tolong bicara lagi, Pak Jaksa!

534
00:56:58,414 --> 00:56:59,707
Pak Jaksa!

535
00:57:01,209 --> 00:57:03,628
Jika mereka mendakwanya,

536
00:57:03,711 --> 00:57:06,256
